      <title>SK 集团有望出售越南 Imexpharm 的多数股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/sk-group-is-said-to-explore-selling-majority-stake-in-vietnam-s-imexpharm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，SK 集团正考虑出售其在 Imexpharm Pharmaceutical JSC 的 65% 股份，此前这家越南药品和医疗产品制造商的股价今年飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/sk-group-is-said-to-explore-selling-majority-stake-in-vietnam-s-imexpharm</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 08:24:32 GMT</pubDate>
